snippet: Australians won the top spots in the men’s and women’s races in the annual Empire State Building Run-up on Wednesday night.
abstract: Australians Mark Bourne and Suzy Walsham win men's and women's 2013 Empire State Building Run-up.
lead_paragraph: Australians won the top spots in the men’s and women’s races in the annual Empire State Building Run-up on Wednesday night.
